{
  "stem": "15014.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was buying a little bit of butter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To have butter was a death sentence, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I wore something like this here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I, I bought butter for this, my cousin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we were coming back to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They stop us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They're going to look what we have.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when came to me, they, they took out a few people that they have something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we never saw these people back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they come-- came to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this German asked me, what do you have there?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[POINTS] Here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, butter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I figure out if he will look anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I have a chance if I say butter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I wouldn't have a chance at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, go!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You are not going to make jokes from me!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Go!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I pass.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he didn't look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had the butter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So this was luck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, it was not smartness.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was pure luck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Or the way how I was in this other town, you know, going up with the-- you know, on the mountain with the-- and my papers were not signed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was luck.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because this guy, all of a sudden, he didn't think at all, you know, that was checking the documents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So everything was luck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- you know, once I went-- was going through the street in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And somebody had a little flowerpot-- not little, big-- without flowers, on the balcony.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It fall down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It just scratch me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this was such luck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It could hit me and kill me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were sitting home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I felt wind, right?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some-- the Germans were shooting.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
